title: Anastasia
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Israeli
description: Vegan cafe in the city center. Owners are vegan and offer healthy food. Raw and gluten-free items marked. Several breakfast options plus salads, sandwiches, mains, and many desserts. Makes onsite soy, almond, and rice milk, and there is a little shop selling vegan food.
